Kissena Boulevard, at the S.W. corner of Elder Ave., showing the home of the son of L. Littlejohn which was erected in 1914 upon the land once owned by J.K Graham in 1873. Note the southern architecture of the house.
January 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
